# Tech Stack

## Frontend

### Web Application
- Framework: Next.js dengan JavaScript
  - Server-side rendering
  - Client-side rendering
  - API routes
- UI Library: React
  - Concurrent rendering
  - Server Components
  - Suspense

### State Management
- Global: Redux Toolkit
  - Predictable state
  - Immutable updates
  - DevTools
- Local: React Context
- Persistence: Redux Persist

### Data Fetching
- Remote: React Query
  - Server state
  - Caching
  - Pagination
- Real-time: SWR
- Optimistic Updates

### Form Handling
- Management: React Hook Form
- Validation: Zod
- Alternative: Yup

### Styling
- Framework: Tailwind CSS
- Processing: PostCSS
- Scoping: CSS Modules
- Dynamic: Emotion/Styled Components

### UI Components
- Library: Custom (Atomic Design)
- Accessibility: Shadcn UI
- Complex: Radix UI
- Development: Storybook

### Data Visualization
- Charts: Recharts
- Advanced: D3.js
- Statistical: Victory Charts

### Mapping
- Rendering: Mapbox GL JS
- Analysis: Turf.js
- Visualization: Deck.gl

## Backend

### Core
- Runtime: Node.js
