  - Validation
- Cache: Redis
  - Rate limiting
  - Job queue
  - Pub/sub

### Storage
- Object: Minio (S3)
- Image: Sharp
- PDF: PDFKit

### Testing
- Unit: Jest
- API: Supertest
- Mocking: Sinon
- Data: Factory/Fixture

### Monitoring
